            </li>
            <li class = "nav-item">
              <a class = "nav-link" href="#danny" role = "tab" data-toggle ="tab">Cancel / Delay FLight</a>
            </li>
            <li class = "nav-item">
              <a class = "nav-link active" href="#agumbe" role = "tab" data-toggle ="tab">Discounted Flight</a>
            </li>                                          
          </ul>
          <div class ="tab-content">
            <div role = "tabpanel"class = "tab-pane fade show active" id = "peter">
              <h3>Schedule Flights For Approval</h3>
              <ul class="list-unstyled" >
                 <li><i class="ri-check-double-line" style="color:#d9232d"></i>Select Your Suitable Destination </li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Decide Your Departure Time</li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Fix Your Flights Rates</li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Provide Discounts If Any </li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Mention Seats For Both Economic And Business Class</li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Request Airline Scheduler For Approval</li>               
              </ul>                        
            </div>
            <div role = "tabpanel"class = "tab-pane fade" id = "danny">
              <h3>Delay Flights,Cancel Flights</h3>
              <ul class="list-unstyled" >
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line" style="color:#d9232d"></i>If You Are In Any Emergency </li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>And You Think It's Necessary To Delay</li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Just Enter Flight Number And New Departure Time</li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>If You Want To Cancel Your Flight </li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Mention Your Flight Number , Departure Time</li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Your Application Will Be Reviewed By Scheduler</li>         
              </ul> 
            </div>
            <div role = "tabpanel"class = "tab-pane fade" id = "agumbe">
              <h3>Flights With Discounted Rates</h3>
              <ul class="list-unstyled" >
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line" style="color:#d9232d"></i>If You Have Attract Passengers </li>
                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"style="color:#d9232d"></i>Provide Discounts , Deals On Tickets</li>
